dback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 22, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104han1665702673003.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/han1665702673003.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/han1665702673003.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"han1665702673003\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Location of the Uniface project directory created during installation.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"han1665702673003__topic_d145067e1_d145068e1_d145069e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"han1665702673003__p_d145070e1_d145071e1_d145072e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">Project</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">DirectoryPath</var>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"han1665702673003__section_w3138ab1b5b3_w3139ab1b5_w3140ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"han1665702673003__table_d17654e1_d17655e1_d17656e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">C:/Users/<var class=\"keyword varname\">UserAccount</var>/Uniface\n                              <var class=\"keyword varname\">Version</var>/project</code> (Windows ) or\n                                 <p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">UnifaceDir</var>/common/project</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">File section: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"efz1665702672861.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/efz1665702672861.html\" title=\"The [install] section of the initialization file contains information about the current installation.\">[install]</a>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"han1665702673003__section_msp_t2p_xvb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d248888e121\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">This directory is the default working directory for Uniface. It contains the\n               <span class=\"ph filepath\">/dbms</span> subdirectory where the default Repository database is\n            located.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">You can configure Uniface to use a different working directory using the\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">WorkDir</span> setting or <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/dir</span> command line switch,\n            and different databases or database locations using path and connector assignments.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sbg1665702735473.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Paths and Path Assignments</a><p>A path is a named route to a resource required by the application, such as a database connector and database, a remote server, or a file location.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/egk1665702698551.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>WorkDir</a><p>Specifies the name of the working directory during the Uniface session.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zvr1665702548679.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>/dir</a><p>Specify the working directory for a Uniface application.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528120\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528120\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Project Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 22, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Location of the Uniface project directory created during installation. Project = DirectoryPath Default value: C:/Users/ UserAccount /Uniface Version /project (Windows ) or UnifaceDir /common/project File section: [install] Description This directory is the default working directory for Uniface. It contains the /dbms subdirectory where the default Repository database is located. You can configure Uniface to use a different working directory using the WorkDir setting or /dir command line switch, and different databases or database locations using path and connector assignments. Related Links Paths and Path Assignments A path is a named route to a resource required by the application, such as a database connector and database, a remote server, or a file location. WorkDir Specifies the name of the working directory during the Uniface session. /dir Specify the working directory for a Uniface application. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}